* add option to enable click-through on friendly nameplates when they are
automatically shown (disabled by default)
* boss mods can now display more than one aura
* fix boss mods compatibility with DBM 7.1.14 and BigWigs 44
* fix some issues related to tracking of boss auras on hidden frames
* fix lua error if DisableFriendlyNameplates is sent before any auras are shown

CALLBACK CHANGES
- Auras:PostCreateAuraButton and Auras:DisplayAura now include the aura frame
as the first argument
